      <title>一季度中国吸收外资锐减56%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/foreign-investment-into-china-slumps-56-in-first-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上季度外国企业对中国的直接投资再次下滑，突显了中国在北京寻求更多海外资金来帮助其经济之际面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/foreign-investment-into-china-slumps-56-in-first-quarter</guid>
